pcapng-utils (1.1.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Feat: Support WebSocket protocol
  * Fix: compatibility upto tshark v4.6 (forky)
  * Fix/Feat: recover orphan HTTP1 responses when tshark was unable to do it automatically (esp. for '206 Partial Content')
  * Feat: stacktrace enrichment -> automatic time-shift from Pirogue `experiment.json` metadata by default
  * Feat: be able to switch off default Pirogue enrichments in CLI
  * Feat: Improve tshark wrapper command and add `dump_tshark_layers_as_json` CLI for intermediate inspection
  * Refact: Nest tshark wrapper configuration under `pcapng_to_har` CLI
  * Config: Use more sensible default for tshark name resolution flags (`-N nds`)
  * Config: Do not require HAR to be dumped as ASCII by default
  * Refact: Reduce code duplication in tshark layers handling
  * Chore: Improve logging (scoped to `pcapng_utils` + repeatable `-v` flag to increase verbosity)
  * Config: HAR creator metadata revision (name and enrichment_files keys)
  * Bump tyro to v1.0

